  <brief_title>Pilot Trial of Intravenous Vitamin C in Refractory Non-Hodgkin Lymphoma (NHL)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Trial of High Dose Intravenous Vitamin C in Patients With Refractory Non-Hodgkin Lymphoma</official_title>
